  <!-- Section 5: Complexity -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">⚡ How Fast Is It?</div>
    <p class="section-desc">Don't worry about the jargon — here's what it means in plain English.</p>

    <div class="analogy-grid">
      <div class="analogy-card">
        <div style="font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:3rem;color:var(--green);letter-spacing:0.05em">O(n)</div>
        <h3>Time Complexity</h3>
        <p>The algorithm looks at each bar exactly once (or twice in the precompute approach). If you double the number of bars, it takes roughly double the time — very efficient!</p>
